verses.text: Naecnab'i, manh jantacoc swach'il schaan sb'a yaj eb' sk'ab' yoc sb'a ayic junnhej tz'aj spensar eb'.
Lajan yet' jun perfume manh jantacoc swach'il scot jililoc t'a sjolom winhaj sacerdote Aarón, tz'emul t'a xil sti' winh, tz'emk'och t'a spayual sjaj spichul winh.
Lajan val icha yal ak'val tz'em t'a sjolom lum vitzal Hermón, tz'empax t'a lum tzalan Sion. Ha b'aj ay junk'olal chi', syak'b'at swach'k'olal Jehová, aton q'uinal t'a junelnhej.
